== 克隆/拉取 ==

拉回项目
git clone https://github.com/Hyman127/hy127v5.11_multi-orchestration.git

例：
git clone https://github.com/Hyman127/hy127v5.11_multi-orchestration.git
git clone git@github.com:Hyman127/hy127v5.11_multi-orchestration.git  
# 会在当前目录下生成 hy127v5.11_multi-orchestration 文件夹

克隆到指定目录
git clone https://github.com/Hyman127/hy127v5.11_multi-orchestration.git my-project
# 会克隆到 my-project 文件夹



